#: phplib/votingarea.php:337
msgid ""
"The District Council is responsible for\n"
"            <strong>local services</strong>, including <strong>planning</strong>, <strong>council housing</strong>, and\n"
"            <strong>rubbish collection</strong>."
msgstr "Mae'r Cyngor Dosbarth yn gyfrifol am <strong>wasanaethau lleol</strong>, gan gynnwys <strong>cynllunio</strong>, <strong>tai cyngor</strong>, a <strong>chasglu sbwriel</strong>."

#: phplib/votingarea.php:340
msgid ""
"\n"
"The Borough Council is responsible for <strong>local services</strong>,\n"
"including <strong>planning</strong>, <strong>council housing</strong>,\n"
"<strong>rubbish collection</strong>, <strong>local roads</strong>, and\n"
"<strong>public paths</strong>.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Mae'r Cyngor Bwrdeistrefol yn gyfrifol am <strong>wasanaethau lleol</strong>, gan gynnwys <strong>cynllunio</strong>, <strong>tai cyngor</strong>, <strong>casglu ysbwriel</strong>, <strong>ffyrdd lleol</strong>, a <strong>llwybrau cyhoeddus</strong>.\n"

#: phplib/votingarea.php:346
msgid ""
"\n"
"Areas covered include the\n"
"Mayor's budget, <strong>culture</strong>, <strong>sport and tourism</strong>,\n"
"<strong>health</strong>, <strong>planning</strong>, <strong>transport</strong>,\n"
"and <strong>trunk roads</strong>.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Dyma’r meysydd a gwmpesir yn cynnwys cyllideb y Maer, <strong>diwylliant</strong>, <strong>chwaraeon a thwristiaeth</strong>, <strong>iechyd</strong>, <strong>cynllunio</strong>, <strong>trafnidiaeth</strong>, a <strong>phriffyrdd</strong>.\n"

#: phplib/votingarea.php:353
msgid ""
"The Metropolitan District Council is\n"
"responsible for all aspects of <strong>local services and policy</strong>, including\n"
"<strong>planning</strong>, <strong>transport</strong>,\n"
"<strong>roads</strong> (except trunk roads and motorways), public rights of way,\n"
"<strong>education</strong>, <strong>social services</strong> and <strong>libraries</strong>."
msgstr "Mae'r Cyngor Dosbarth Prifddinesig yn gyfrifol am bob agwedd o <strong>bolisi a gwasanaethau lleol</strong>, gan gynnwys <strong>cynllunio</strong>, <strong>trafnidiaeth</strong>, <strong>ffyrdd</strong> (heblaw priffyrdd a thraffyrdd), hawliau tramwy cyhoeddus, <strong>addysg</strong>, <strong>gwasanaethau cymdeithasol</strong> a <strong>llyfrgelloedd</strong>."

#: phplib/votingarea.php:359
msgid ""
"The Unitary Authority is\n"
"responsible for all aspects of <strong>local services and policy</strong>, including\n"
"<strong>planning</strong>, <strong>transport</strong>,\n"
"<strong>roads</strong> (except trunk roads and motorways), public rights of way,\n"
"<strong>education</strong>, <strong>social services</strong> and <strong>libraries</strong>."
msgstr "Mae'r Awdurdod Unedol yn gyfrifol am bob agwedd o <strong>bolisi a gwasanaethau lleol</strong>, gan gynnwys <strong>cynllunio</strong>, <strong>trafnidiaeth</strong>, <strong>ffyrdd</strong> (heblaw priffyrdd a thraffyrdd), hawliau tramwy cyhoeddus, <strong>addysg</strong>, <strong>gwasanaethau cymdeithasol</strong> a <strong>llyfrgelloedd</strong>."

#: phplib/votingarea.php:364
msgid ""
"\n"
"The Council of the Isles is responsible for <strong>education</strong>,\n"
"<strong>housing</strong>, <strong>planning</strong>, <strong>water and\n"
"sewage</strong> and various other local matters including\n"
"<strong>tourism</strong>, <strong>development</strong> and running <strong>the\n"
"airport</strong>.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Mae Cyngor yr Ynysoedd yn gyfrifol am <strong>addysg</strong>, <strong>tai</strong>, <strong>cynllunio</strong>, <strong>dŵr a charthffosiaeth</strong> ac amryw o faterion lleol eraill gan gynnwys <strong>twristiaeth</strong>, <strong>datblygu</strong> a rheoli’r <strong>maes awyr</strong>.\n"

#: phplib/votingarea.php:372 templates/website/yourrep/ced.html:1
msgid ""
"The County Council is responsible for <strong>local\n"
"services</strong>, including <strong>education</strong>, <strong>social services</strong>,\n"
"<strong>transport</strong>, <strong>roads</strong>\n"
"(except trunk roads and motorways), public rights of way, and\n"
"<strong>libraries</strong>."
msgstr "Y Cyngor Sir sy'n gyfrifol am <strong>wasanaethau lleol</strong>, gan gynnwys <strong>addysg</strong>, <strong>gwasanaethau cymdeithasol</strong>, <strong>trafnidiaeth</strong>, <strong>ffyrdd</strong> (heblaw priffyrdd a thraffyrdd), hawliau tramwy cyhoeddus, a <strong>llyfrgelloedd</strong>."

#: phplib/votingarea.php:378
msgid ""
"The Local Council is responsible for\n"
"            <strong>local services</strong>, including \n"
"            <strong>waste and recycling</strong>, \n"
"            <strong>leisure and community</strong>, \n"
"            <strong>building control</strong> and\n"
"            <strong>local economic and cultural development</strong>."
msgstr "Mae'r Cyngor Lleol yn gyfrifol am <strong>wasanaethau lleol</strong>, gan gynnwys <strong>gwastraff ac ailgylchu</strong>, <strong>hamdden a chymuned</strong>, <strong>rheoli adeiladu</strong> a <strong>datblygu economaidd a diwylliannol lleol</strong>."

#: phplib/votingarea.php:385
msgid ""
"The House of Commons is responsible for\n"
"            <strong>making laws in the UK and for overall scrutiny of all aspects of\n"
"            government</strong>."
msgstr "Mae Tŷ'r Cyffredin yn gyfrifol am <strong>greu cyfraith yn y DU ac am graffu cyffredinol ar bob agwedd ar lywodraeth</strong>."

#: phplib/votingarea.php:388
msgid ""
"\n"
"They <strong>scrutinise proposed European laws</strong> and the <strong>budget of the\n"
"European Union</strong>, and provide <strong>oversight of its other\n"
"decision-making bodies</strong>.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Maent yn <strong>gwyntyllu cyfreithiau Ewropeaidd arfaethedig</strong> a <strong>chyllideb yr Undeb Ewropeaidd</strong>, ac yn darparu <strong>goruchwyliaeth o'i gyrff sy’n gyfrifol am benderfyniadau eraill</strong>.\n"

#: phplib/votingarea.php:393
msgid ""
"\n"
"The Scottish Parliament is responsible for a wide range of <strong>devolved\n"
"matters</strong> in which it sets policy independently of the London\n"
"Parliament. Devolved matters include <strong>education</strong>,\n"
"<strong>health</strong>, <strong>agriculture</strong>, <strong>justice</strong>\n"
"and <strong>prisons</strong>. It also has some tax-raising powers.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Mae Senedd yr Alban yn gyfrifol am ystod eang o <strong>faterion datganoledig</strong> lle mae'n gosod polisi yn annibynnol o Senedd San Steffan yn Llundain. Mae materion datganoledig yn cynnwys <strong>addysg</strong>, <strong>iechyd</strong>, <strong>amaethyddiaeth</strong>, <strong>cyfiawnder</strong> a <strong>charchardai</strong>. Mae ganddi hefyd rai pwerau codi trethi.\n"

#: phplib/votingarea.php:400
msgid ""
"\n"
"The Senedd has a wide range of powers over areas including\n"
"<strong>economic development</strong>, <strong>transport</strong>,\n"
"<strong>finance</strong>, <strong>local government</strong>,\n"
"<strong>health</strong>, <strong>housing</strong> and <strong>the Welsh\n"
"Language</strong>.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Mae gan Y Senedd ystod eang o rymoedd dros feysydd gan gynnwys <strong>datblygiad economaidd</strong>, <strong>trafnidiaeth</strong>, <strong>cyllid</strong>, <strong>llywodraeth leol</strong>, <strong>iechyd</strong>, <strong>tai</strong> a’r <strong>iaith Gymraeg</strong>.\n"

#: phplib/votingarea.php:407
msgid ""
"\n"
"The Northern Ireland Assembly has full authority over \"transferred matters\",\n"
"which include <strong>agriculture</strong>, <strong>education</strong>,\n"
"<strong>employment</strong>, the <strong>environment</strong> and\n"
"<strong>health</strong>.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Mae gan Gynulliad Gogledd Iwerddon awdurdod llawn dros \"faterion a drosglwyddwyd\", sy'n cynnwys <strong>amaethyddiaeth</strong>, <strong>addysg</strong>, <strong>cyflogaeth</strong>, yr <strong>amgylchledd</strong> ac <strong>iechyd</strong>.\n"

