#: templates/website/problem-lords-similar.html:22
msgid "Sorry, but we have to limit the number of similar messages sent to members of the House of Lords, as they have told us they simply disregard more than a handful messages of substantially identical content arriving within a couple of days."
msgstr "Mae'n ddrwg gennym, ond mae'n rhaid i ni gyfyngu ar nifer y negeseuon tebyg a anfonir at aelodau o Dŷ'r Arglwyddi, gan eu bod wedi dweud wrthym eu bod yn anwybyddu mwy na llond llaw o negeseuon sydd â chynnwys sy’n arbennig o debyg ac yn cyrraedd mewn ychydig ddyddiau."

#: templates/website/problem-lords-similar.html:24
msgid "If you wish to try again, please use the \"back\" button in your browser and rewrite your message."
