msgid "You seem to be sending messages with several different postcodes"
msgstr "Mae'n ymddangos eich bod chi'n anfon negeseuon gyda sawl cod post gwahanol"

#: templates/website/problem-postcodes.html:22
msgid "Sorry, but please read <a href=\"/about-qa#onlyrep\">this</a> to understand why our site only lets you write to <em>your own elected representatives</em>, not those for other parts of the country."
msgstr "Mae'n ddrwg gennym, ond darllenwch <a href=\"/about-qa#onlyrep\">this</a> i ddeall pam mae ein gwefan ond yn gadael i chi ysgrifennu at <em>eich cynrychiolwyr etholedig eich hun</em>, nid y rhai ar gyfer rhannau eraill o'r wlad."

#: templates/website/problem-postcodes.html:24
msgid "If we didn’t do this, then representatives would be snowed under with mail from all and sundry, and that would mean they ignored the important mail from their own constituents. They might even bin <strong>all</strong> messages sent via WriteToThem.com."
msgstr "Os na wnaethom hyn, yna byddai cynrychiolwyr yn cael post gan bawb, a buasai hynny'n golygu eu bod yn anwybyddu'r post pwysig gan eu hetholwyr eu hunain. Efallai y byddant hyd yn oed yn anwybyddu’r <cryf>holl</cryf> negeseuon a anfonir trwy WriteToThem.com."

#: templates/website/problem-postcodes.html:26
msgid "Either of which would be A Bad Thing."
msgstr "Buasai’r naill neu'r llall yn beth drwg."

#: templates/website/problem-postcodes.html:28
msgid "If somebody else suggested that you do this to get their message across, you might want to let them know potentially sabotaged their own campaign too. Perhaps you might ask them to read the <a href=\"/about-guidelines\">instructions</a> on the site next time?"
msgstr "Os yw rhywun arall yn awgrymu eich bod chi'n gwneud hyn i gyfleu eu neges, efallai yr hoffech chi roi gwybod iddynt o bosibl fod wedi niweidio eu hymgyrch eu hunain hefyd. Efallai gallwch ofyn iddyn nhw ddarllen y <a href=\"/about-guidelines\">cyfarwyddiadau</a> ar y wefan y tro nesaf?"

#: templates/website/problem-postcodes.html:30
msgid "If you wish to send a message, please <a href=\"/\">start again from the beginning</a> and give only your own, real address and postcode when asked."
msgstr "Os hoffech anfon neges, <a href=\"/\">dechrau o'r dechrau</a> a rhowch eich cyfeiriad a'ch cod post eich hun yn unig"

#: templates/website/problem-similar.html:14
msgid "Your message is near-identical to others sent previously"
msgstr "Mae eich neges bron yn union yr un fath ag eraill sydd eisoes wedi eu danfon"

#: templates/website/problem-similar.html:22
msgid "Please read <a href=\"/about-qa#formletters\">our stance on this issue</a> to understand why sending identikit \"copied and pasted\" messages is detrimental to your campaign."
msgstr "Darllenwch <a href=\"/about-qa#formletters\">ein safbwynt ar y mater hwn</a> i ddeall pam mae anfon negeseuon \"torri a gludo\" yn niweidiol i'ch ymgyrch."

#: templates/website/problem-similar.html:24
msgid "Sorry to be so harsh, but representatives have made it clear that the receipt of such \"spam\" could mean they bin <strong>all</strong> messages sent via WriteToThem.com."
msgstr "Mae'n ddrwg gennym fod mor llym, ond mae cynrychiolwyr wedi ei gwneud hi’n glir y gallai derbyn \"sbam\" o'r fath olygu eu bod yn anwybyddu yr <strong>holl</strong> negeseuon a anfonir trwy WriteToThem.com."

#: templates/website/problem-similar.html:26
msgid "Which would be A Bad Thing."
msgstr "A buasai hynny’n beth drwg."

#: templates/website/problem-similar.html:28
msgid "You might like to let the person who asked you to do this know that they’ve potentially sabotaged their own campaign too. Point them to our <a href=\"/about-guidelines\">Guidelines for campaigning</a>."
msgstr "Efallai yr hoffech adael i'r person a ofynnodd i chi wneud hyn wybod eu bod o bosibl wedi niweidio eu hymgyrch eu hunain hefyd. Rhowch wybod i nhw am ein <a href=\"/about-guidelines\">Canllawiau ar gyfer ymgyrchu</a>."

#: templates/website/problem-similar.html:30
msgid "If you wish to rewrite your message, use the \"back\" button in your browser and write it in your own, original, words. It’s better to send a short message in your own words, than a long, mainly copy-and-pasted message with a few amendments."
msgstr "Os hoffech ailysgrifennu'ch neges, defnyddiwch y botwm \"yn ôl\" yn eich porwr a'i ysgrifennu yn eich geiriau gwreiddiol eich hun. Mae'n well anfon neges fer yn eich geiriau eich hun, na neges hir wedi’i thorri a gludo ac yna wedi’i addasu."

