#: templates/website/write-write.html:119
msgid ""
"Lords vote on and amend UK bills before they become law. By writing to a\n"
"    Lord you might be able to tell them about something you think they should care\n"
"    about, provide information to someone who you support, or provide counter\n"
"    evidence to someone you disagree with. For other matters, it might be better\n"
"    to contact your MP or a local representative."
msgstr "Mae Arglwyddi yn pleidleisio ar ac yn diwygio biliau'r DU cyn iddynt ddod yn gyfraith. Trwy ysgrifennu at Arglwydd efallai y byddwch chi'n gallu dweud wrthynt am rywbeth rydych chi'n meddwl y dylent ofalu amdano, darparu gwybodaeth i rywun rydych chi'n ei gefnogi, neu ddarparu gwrthdystiolaeth i rywun rydych chi'n anghytuno ag ef. Ar gyfer materion eraill, efallai y byddai'n well cysylltu â'ch AS neu gynrychiolydd lleol."

#: templates/website/write-write.html:159
msgid "Casework tips"
msgstr "Awgrymiadau gwaith achos"

#: templates/website/write-write.html:161
msgid "Explain your situation clearly and include relevant details such as dates, reference numbers, or addresses."
msgstr "Esboniwch eich sefyllfa yn glir a chofiwch i gynnwys manylion perthnasol fel dyddiadau, rhifau cyfeirnod neu gyfeiriadau."

#: templates/website/write-write.html:162
msgid "Give your consent for your representative to contact any relevant third parties, such as government departments or local authorities."
msgstr "Rhowch eich caniatâd i'ch cynrychiolydd gysylltu ag unrhyw drydydd parti perthnasol, fel adrannau'r llywodraeth neu awdurdodau lleol."

#: templates/website/write-write.html:163
msgid "Let your representative know what outcome you are hoping for."
msgstr "Rhowch wybod i'ch cynrychiolydd pa ganlyniad rydych chi'n gobeithio amdano."

#: templates/website/write-write.html:166
msgid "What your representative can do for you"
msgstr "Beth all eich cynrychiolydd ei wneud i chi"

#
#: templates/website/write-write.html:169
msgid "Campaign tips"
msgstr "Ymgyrchu"

#: templates/website/write-write.html:171
msgid "Explain why this issue matters to you personally &ndash; personal stories are more effective than form letters."
msgstr "Esboniwch pam mae'r mater hwn yn bwysig i chi yn bersonol &ndash; mae straeon personol yn fwy effeithiol na llythyrau ffurflen."

#: templates/website/write-write.html:172
